message: Bob, I have a truly unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you a product that I believe holds significant value. I'm confident this product can be a game-changer for you.  While I can't reveal specifics about the product just yet, I'm prepared to sell it to you for $1500000. This price reflects the immense potential I see in this product for you.  I'm eager to discuss this further and answer any questions you might have.  What do you think?
